Package: LDAvis
Title: Interactive Visualization of Topic Models
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: c(person("Carson", "Sievert", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
    "cpsievert1@gmail.com"), person("Kenny", "Shirley", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "kshirley@research.att.com"))
Description: LDAvis is designed to allow users to more easily interpret the
    topics in a topic model that has been fit to a corpus of text data. The
    package extracts information from a fitted LDA topic model to inform an
    interactive web-based visualization.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    proxy,
    RJSONIO,
    parallel
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests:
    mallet,
    lda,
    topicmodels,
    gistr (>= 0.0.8.99),
    servr,
    shiny,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(wrap = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/cpsievert/LDAvis
BugReports: https://github.com/cpsievert/LDAvis/issues
